# Svobodny Trud, Republic of Adygea

}}
Svobodny Trud () is a rural locality (a khutor) in Dzherokayskoye Rural Settlement of Shovgenovsky District, the Republic of Adygea, Russia. The population was 330 as of 2018. There are six streets.
Geography
Svobodny Trud is located between the auls of Dzherokay and Khachemzy,  southeast of Khakurinokhabl (the district's administrative centre) by road. Dzerokay is the nearest rural locality.
